        <%= image_tag 'miked.png', class: 'img-fluid about-image' %>
        <br />
        <p class="about-names">Mike Dunnett-Stone</p>
        <p>
        Mike is the founder of <%= link_to 'Seed Music', 'www.seedmusic.co.uk' %>, a social enterprise that provides music practice rooms for offices. Previously, he was a senior strategy consultant and holds a starred 1st in Politics, Philosophy and Economics (PPE). He can often be found floundering at the piano.</p>
        <div class="text-center">
          <%= link_to 'https://github.com/mdunnettstone' do %>
