        Denise is an aspiring web developer with an emphasis on Ruby on Rails. With a Bachelor of Arts degree in Business Administration, most of her career has focused on accounting and financial anaylsis. Denise describes herself as an itinerant adventurer, world traveler, tree hugger and all around superb human being. </p>
