        Tristen is a teacher-turned-techie with a passion for the intentional use of technology in education. Her dream is to build meaningful experiential learning tools for students, and systems to assist teachers in their practice and help them better prepare young populations for responsible digital citizenship. Educational technology allows an infinite number of learning experiences to be accessible for those students who may not have access otherwise. She also loves her cat and naps on the beach. </p>
